498
00:29:12,860 --> 00:29:13,760
Itu kamu.

499
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:16,830
[Xie Zheng, Marquis dari Wu'an]

500
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,750
[Xie Zheng, Marquis dari Wu'an]

501
00:29:21,770 --> 00:29:24,790
[Xie Zheng]

502
