530
00:30:40,690 --> 00:30:41,540
Omong kosong!

531
00:30:42,890 --> 00:30:43,820
Ayahku berkata

532
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:45,760
Dia memimpin pasukan.

533
00:30:46,220 --> 00:30:48,180
